@Skype1 wrote:

case 9167: if(c.teleEffect == 1) c.triggerTele(3296, 3649, 0);// hills c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); if(c.teleEffect == 2) c.triggerTele(3039, 4834, 0);// Abyss c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); break; case 9168: if(c.teleEffect == 1) c.triggerTele(3244, 3518, 0);// Varrock Wild c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); if(c.teleEffect == 2) c.closeInterface(); break; case 9169: if(c.teleEffect == 1) c.triggerTele(2539+misc.random(2), 4716+misc.random(2), 0);// Mage Bank c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); break;

You may want to save the other codes so you can remember the coords however to teleport to one major city the code would look like this…

case 9167: c.triggerTele(XCOORD, YCOORD, 0); break;
